Package com.example.habitup.View

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EventListAdapter.OnItemClickListener  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddHabitActivity
    This is the activity to add a habit.
    AddHabitEventActivity
    This is the activity for adding a habit event.
    AttributeAdapter
    This is the adapter for creating a dropdown spinner menu for attributes during a create habit activity.
    BaseActivity
    This is the main parent activity class for other activities that need access to the drawer navigation layout.
    EditHabitActivity
    This is the activity for editing a habit.
    EditHabitEventActivity
    This is the activity for editing a habit event.
    EditProfileActivity
    This is the activity for editing the current user's profile fields.
    EventListAdapter
    This is the adapter for creating the list of habit events, which displays the event's habit name, icons to display whether the event has an image and location, the event's comment, and the event's completion date.
    FindUserActivity
    This activity will search for other users by username or full name.
    FollowActivity
    This activity will display all the user's current follow requests.
    FollowRequestAdapter
    This is the adapter for displaying the user's follow requests.
    FollowRequestAdapter.FollowRequestHolder  
    HabitListAdapter
    This is the adapter for creating the habit list, which displays the habit name, and it's schedule.
    HabitStatistics
    This activity displays the user habit statistics, such as progression statuses for all habits.
    LoginActivity
    This is the the start up launch activity where the user can login into the HabitUp application.
    MainActivity
    This is the main activity for the HabitUp application.
    MapActivity
    This activity displays a map where the user can view the locations of their filtered habit events, locations of friends' events, or location of the nearest habit events.
    ProfileHabitsAdapter
    This is the adapter for the habits that will be displayed in a user's profile screen.
    SignUpActivity
    This is the activity for signing up for a new user account.
    ViewFriendsActivity
    This activity displays a list of the user's friends and their habits.
    ViewHabitActivity
    This is the activity where all the user's habits are displayed alphabetically by habit name.
    ViewHabitEventActivity
    This is the activity where the user can see their habit event history, which displays a list of all the habit events completed, sorted by most recent date.
